PitokTube

PitokTube is a next-generation social media platform that combines:

* TikTok-style short video feed
* Telegram-style messaging
* YouTube-style creator profiles
* Pi Network authentication and payments

MVP Features

* Pi Login
* Short video upload
* Vertical feed
* Like & Comment
* Follow users
* One-to-one messaging
* Pi tipping

Status: 🚧 Under Development